934 831 M 
-0.121 0 (Doc No. 97-0024R1, N1062R1)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 981 M 
-0.012 0 (On Tuesday we had the discussion of what the core solution should look like. Here is the outcome:)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1081 M 
0.053 0 (At present clause 14 does not say anything about whether and when default argument expressions of)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1131 M 
0.108 0 (template function specializations are instantiated. There may have been discussion and solutions in)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1181 M 
0.094 0 (CoreIII, but they did not get into the WP. What we do have in the WP are:)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1281 M 
0.055 0 (14.7.3/3: An explicit specialization is not allowed to have default arguments, so we do not have to bother)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1331 M 
0.061 0 (about them.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1381 M 
0.091 0 (8.3.6/4 specifies a rule for default arguments of templates, but that is not important for our issue.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1481 M 
0.173 0 (14.7.1/6 and 14.8.3: A declaration is instantiated if it is used as a candidate function. Since this also)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1531 M 
0.052 0 (happens if the function is not going to be called, we decided to leave this rule alone.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1631 M 
0.094 0 (14.6.4.2: This was introduced to allow an instantiation take place using the debugger symbol table at)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1681 M 
0.093 0 (runtime. No wording in there exists which precludes it being applied to default arguments as well. So if)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1731 M 
0.137 0 (we fix a point where a default argument should be instantiated, this paragraph automatically allows an)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1781 M 
0.103 0 (implementation to use the global program as a substitute.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1831 M 
-0.049 0 (The words about )A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco %%IncludeFont: Times-Italic
(F5) cvn
