588 1831 M 
0.112 0 (with external linkage)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
945 1831 M 
-0.043 0 ( have been noticed by coreIII to be a problem. A solution to them)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1881 M 
0.011 0 (should affect both the function body and default arguments.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1931 M 
0.072 0 (Applying these rules to default arguments in the present state may disallow the use of static functions in)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 1981 M 
0.109 0 (default arguments, but that is a very small price to pay and I am very willing to do that.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2081 M 
0.139 0 (What also occurred to us is that we need the understanding that the declaration of a template function)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2131 M 
0.120 0 (creates a definition context for that function. This is the context where the phase 1 name binding occurs)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2181 M 
0.105 0 (and that is done both for function definitions as well as function declarations. This is a problem)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2231 M 
0.164 0 (independent of the topic at hand.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2281 M 
0.055 0 (I do not know whether we need wording in the WP to clarify this.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2381 M 
0.154 0 (When explicitly instantiating a template default arguments are not affected. An explicit instantiation)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2431 M 
0.023 0 (should only affect the body of a function or the initializer \(maybe including constructor call\) of a static)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2481 M 
0.119 0 (data member. Any future work on explicit instantiation should take this into account.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2581 M 
0.121 0 (During the week I realized that every template function specialization has several instantiation points)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2631 M 
0.141 0 (even within a singe translation unit. Every use of the function creates one instantiation point.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2681 M 
0.083 0 (So we do not have to worry about the binding being in a different place than that for the function.)A 
; : 0 0 2391 3229 rc 0 0 0 sco F3_42
Ji 
296 2731 M 
0.095 0 (Wherever a default argument is instantiated, the instantiation of the function body is allowed as well.)A 
; 
